<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AFRAP70A9206001" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Dépose et pose du bloc de phare 
</title>
<attention1>
<ptxt>
Les ampoules de phare peuvent être très chaudes. Il existe un risque de brûlure si vous les touchez sans faire attention. 
</ptxt>
</attention1>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Ne pas toucher la surface de verre de l&#39;ampoule avec des mains nues. La surface de l&#39;ampoule sera salie et sera trouble quand l&#39;ampoule est allumée. 
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Le bloc de phare étant monté sur le véhicule, il est possible de remplacer les ampoules. 
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Après avoir remplacé le bloc de phare et/ou la ou les ampoules de phare, vérifier et régler le phare. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A9206002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "AFRAP70A9206001001">
<title>
Dépose 
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Débrancher le câble négatif (–) de la batterie. 
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Déposer le pare-chocs avant. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A9806001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Débrancher les connecteurs du bloc de phare. 
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Déposer les vis (1) et l&#39;agrafe de bloc de phare, puis déposer le bloc de phare (2). 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70P920007.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "69.820mm" ver = "01" gw = "206" gh = "181"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Déposer les ampoules, si nécessaire. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70P920041.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "68.513mm" ver = "02" gw = "212" gh = "178"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.237in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.402in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.216in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.601in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ampoule de feu de position 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
4. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Douille d&#39;ampoule de clignotant 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ampoule de clignotant 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
5. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Douille d&#39;ampoule de feu de position 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ampoule de phare 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
6. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Cache de douille 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AFRAP70A9206001002">
<title>
Repose 
</title>
<ptxt>
Procéder dans l&#39;ordre inverse de la dépose en notant les points suivants. 
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Reposer l&#39;agrafe de bloc de phare. 
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Poser les vis (1, &#34;1&#34; – 1, &#34;4&#34;) dans l&#39;ordre numérique indiqué sur le schéma. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A920008.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "69.820mm" ver = "02" gw = "206" gh = "181"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.426in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MADONOT" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ne pas réutiliser. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
